txt.en: You have explored many wondrous locations within Lothlórien.
You have stood watch upon the many flets of Lothlórien.
There are many opportunities to perform great deeds for the Galadhrim of Lothlórien.
You have explored the ways of Caras Galadhon, the city of the Lord and Lady of the Galadhrim.
You have hunted many beasts in the woods of Lothlórien.
You have defeated many of Mazog's minions in the names of the Lord and Lady.
Complete Wanderer of the Golden Wood
Complete City of the Lord and Lady
